    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Iron Corbo 是一款厚颜无耻的动作冒险游戏。与华丽的终结者一起定制您自己的功夫组合。扫荡、清理和粉碎你的方式，穿过这个滑稽、非线性、后文明的嬉闹游戏，带有轻微的类银河战士恶魔城元素。成为扫帚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与科博一起，他已经过了巅峰期，陷入了可怕的困境，他每天都在清理街上的垃圾。在这个奇特的故事中，揭开机器人为何如此顽皮的谜团。🌎🌍🌏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185250/extras/5d441d5d2e1b1748fda99ac7695ccb45.poster.avif?t=1770592128\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185250/extras/5d441d5d2e1b1748fda99ac7695ccb45.webm?t=1770592128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185250/extras/5d441d5d2e1b1748fda99ac7695ccb45.mp4?t=1770592128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185250/extras/b0ff4852d1e6239f8a55032d6e8553e5.avif?t=1770592128\" width=600 height=696 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185250/extras/4ab4ac9a7ea8a4a29e41ddab183d3c9e.avif?t=1770592128\" width=600 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185250/extras/7448bc02a6ded668868ee5d4c06a5ac7.avif?t=1770592128\" width=1200 height=674 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185250/extras/0049cc873ec5ed24005adc0ff8b22750.avif?t=1770592128\" width=600 height=107 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185250/extras/5ba245404185bf00b715f5446d66f3c2.poster.avif?t=1770592128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185250/extras/5ba245404185bf00b715f5446d66f3c2.webm?t=1770592128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185250/extras/5ba245404185bf00b715f5446d66f3c2.mp4?t=1770592128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >㊋ 功夫清洁工连招：畅享深度分层的战斗系统，打造专属攻击组合。冒险越多，回报越高。发挥创意，切勿自大，否则科尔博的脸就会被亲吻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >㊋ 敌人遭遇：强悍却公平的对手，解读他们的行动并进行相应的反击。巨型Boss等待着你的考验。向他们展示你的清洁工功夫！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >㊋ 战斗遗物：超过50种独特技能，选择你最喜欢的，以适应特定的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >㊋ 非线性进程：选择如何探索广阔的废弃城市、学校、洞穴、酒店等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >㊋ 玩家选择：你的决定将影响某些故事元素和游戏走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >㊋ 秘密：隐藏的路径可能带来意想不到的发现，也可能带来一些令人叹为观止的垃圾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
